The Long View

In this episode of The Long View, I&#8217;m joined by Joel Eddy as we discuss the game Airlines Europe. During our discussion, we decide if this indeed a gateway game, and just what the Eddy Theory is all about! Thanks, as always, to www.2d6.org for hosting The Long View, a proud member of The Dice Tower Network, and thanks to our sponsor, www.gamesurplus.com, your first and best choice for all of your board gaming needs! Thanks to Joel for his insightful discussion, and thanks, as always, to YOU for listening!
~ Geof Gambill
&#160;
&#160;
&#160;
